tives  Europe's best food experts are joining forces to crack down on fraud.\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3104, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Euronews is following them in this special series: The Food Detectives  Water Matters  Europe's water is under increasing pressure.\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3160, \"end\": 3175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_Detectives\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Food Detectives\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_Detectives\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_Detectives\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pollution, droughts, floods are taking their toll on our drinking water, lakes, rivers and coastlines.\", \"from\": 3237, \"to\": 3339, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join us on a journey around Europe to see why protecting ecosystems matters, how our wastewater can be better managed, and to discover some of the best water solutions.\", \"from\": 3340, \"to\": 3508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Video reports, an animated explainer series and live debate - find out why Water Matters, from Euronews.\", \"from\": 3511, \"to\": 3615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3606, \"end\": 3614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euronews\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Euronews\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euronews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euronews\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Climate Now  We give you the latest climate facts from the world's leading source, analyse the trends and explain how our planet is changing.\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We meet the experts on the front line of climate change who explore new strategies to mitigate and adapt.\", \"from\": 3759, \"to\": 3864, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Uber, the ride-hailing app, announced a list of measures to meet the explosive demand during the upcoming Paris Summer Olympics on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 4007, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A major concern for residents and tourists during the much-anticipated sporting event will be navigating the French capital this summer, as 15 million visitors are expected to strain the public transport networks.\", \"from\": 4009, \"to\": 4222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4118, \"end\": 4124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9121088342677142, \"rank\": 0.095885114417556, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After many rounds of negotiations, Uber said it obtained the right to circulate in some of the most restricted areas of Paris, previously reserved for taxis.\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4344, \"end\": 4349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 1.2433591243168396e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These zones include blue and red areas for picking up or dropping off customers and grey areas for drivers assisting people with mobility issues.\", \"from\": 4383, \"to\": 4528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The company expects a record of 40,000 drivers to provide rides on its platform during theOlympics.\", \"from\": 4530, \"to\": 4629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Uber drivers will not be able to use the \\\"Olympic lanes\\\" referring to the 185 kilometres of roads around Paris reserved for delegations, taxis, buses, and journalists - a major disappointment for both the Uber drivers and the company.\", \"from\": 4631, \"to\": 4874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4745, \"end\": 4750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 1.2433591243168396e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We really feel a discrimination between ride-hailing apps and taxis,\\\" said Karim Daoud, President of the Union representing ride-hailing drivers in France (AVF).\", \"from\": 4876, \"to\": 5038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4952, \"end\": 4957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karim_Wade\", \"score\": 0.9999996790311858, \"rank\": 3.1910073675853713e-07, \"text\": \"Karim\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karim_Wade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karim_Wade\"}, {\"begin\": 4982, \"end\": 4987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.8716656848560866e-12, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 5025, \"end\": 5031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999457738518702, \"rank\": 4.9513603554854754e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 5033, \"end\": 5036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AV_Formula\", \"score\": 0.9999999990309334, \"rank\": 9.682369213448795e-10, \"text\": \"AVF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AV_Formula\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AV_Formula\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Without these reserved lanes, it's going to be very difficult for us to get around.\", \"from\": 5040, \"to\": 5124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am afraid that a lot of drivers will throw in the towel,\\\" he told Euronews.\", \"from\": 5125, \"to\": 5202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5193, \"end\": 5201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euronews\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Euronews\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euronews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euronews\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Daoud hinted at the possibility of a strike of Uber drivers during the sporting event: \\\"We reserve the right to hold protests.\", \"from\": 5204, \"to\": 5333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's still on the agenda but we advocate for some sort of dialogue first.\\\"\", \"from\": 5334, \"to\": 5410, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the passenger side,Uberpromises to contain the surge in prices.\", \"from\": 5412, \"to\": 5478, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the millions of visitors expected in Paris this summer, the price surge will be limited to \\\"10 to 15%\\\", assured Laureline Serieys, the General Manager of Uber in France.\", \"from\": 5479, \"to\": 5656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5524, \"end\": 5529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 1.2433591243168396e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 5599, \"end\": 5608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Val\\u00e9rian_and_Laureline\", \"score\": 0.9999999995666258, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laureline\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Val\\u00e9rian_and_Laureline\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Val\\u00e9rian_and_Laureline\"}, {\"begin\": 5649, \"end\": 5655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999457738518702, \"rank\": 4.9513603554854754e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fares for journeys to and from Paris airports and train stations will be reduced by 10% during the period and the price for the ride-sharing option UberShare will be slashed by 30% during the whole sporting event.\", \"from\": 5658, \"to\": 5871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5689, \"end\": 5694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 1.2433591243168396e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the summer season, Uber will also offer two new experiences to its users.\", \"from\": 5873, \"to\": 5953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5899, \"end\": 5903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uber\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.131977105923774e-28, \"text\": \"Uber\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uber\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uber\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first, \\\"Uber Bubbles\\\", will allow four people to book an excursion in an electric Tesla vehicle to the Champagne region.\", \"from\": 5954, \"to\": 6078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6040, \"end\": 6045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tesla_Model_3\", \"score\": 0.9972983670016848, \"rank\": 0.002708951591368938, \"text\": \"Tesla\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tesla_Model_3\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tesla_Model_3\"}, {\"begin\": 6061, \"end\": 6077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champagne_wine_region\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4254773577432547e-28, \"text\": \"Champagne region\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champagne_wine_region\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champagne_wine_region\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Customers will have two champagne tastings and lunch for 200 euros in total for four people.\", \"from\": 6080, \"to\": 6172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The second experience called \\\"Uber Cruise\\\" will allow customers to book a river cruise on the Seine with a skipper.\", \"from\": 6174, \"to\": 6289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6268, \"end\": 6273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999943835221912, \"rank\": 5.6165021127770904e-06, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There will be five boats available with multiple time slots per day.\", \"from\": 6290, \"to\": 6358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Browse today's tags\", \"from\": 6364, \"to\": 6383, \"entities\": []}]}"